strings:
<voice_0x010011E6><se_high><center>My name is Alex,
<center>I live in the world for many years.
<center>I took this photo with my own hands.

<voice_0x010011E7><se_high><center>Let me tell you a story.
<center>Forgotten moments lost in the vast
<center>ocean of history. The origin of magic...

<voice_0x010011E8><se_high><center>He came from the Cranbartle family.
<center>The family is descended from
<center>one of the legendary seven sages.

<voice_0x010011E9><se_high><center>But my generation has seen the wonderful
<center>legacy passed down through marriage
<center>from the Albert family.
<center>Hi, I have been selected to take a place.

<voice_0x010011EA><se_high><center>The eldest son is always
<center>from the Albert family.

<voice_0x010011EB><se_high><center>But when the life of the last heir,
<center>Alistair, ends, a dark and evil
<center>force destroys this bond...
<voice_0x010011EC><se_high><center>However, I am of the Albert family.
<voice_0x010011ED><se_high><center>So I will do my best to help the Albert family.

<voice_0x010011EE><se_high><center>I want you to remove the marijuana statues
<center>of the Ku Klux Klan. I have no doubt
<center>that you will find them useful.

<voice_0x010011EF><se_high><center>Since then, only Jessica has been able
<center>to inherit the Albert family blood.
<center>please help him
